228
00:13:10,440 --> 00:13:11,160
sa tingin ko

229
00:13:11,160 --> 00:13:12,360
wala na ang kamatayan

230
00:13:12,640 --> 00:13:14,680
isang banta para sa iyo.

231
00:13:14,840 --> 00:13:17,120
Pero yung mga tumulong

232
00:13:17,360 --> 00:13:18,760
mabuhay ka...

233
00:13:19,920 --> 00:13:21,280
Hindi ka lang manonood

234
00:13:21,280 --> 00:13:23,680
mamatay sila dahil sayo, ikaw?

235
00:13:28,400 --> 00:13:29,720
Hindi ko na namalayan

236
00:13:30,200 --> 00:13:31,360
na ang kasalukuyang ako

237
00:13:32,040 --> 00:13:34,280
may halaga pa rin na pinagsasamantalahan mo.

238
00:13:35,360 --> 00:13:37,000
Wala kang saysay dito

239
00:13:37,000 --> 00:13:38,840
sa mansyon.

240
00:13:39,400 --> 00:13:40,720
Ikaw ay buntis,

241
00:13:40,720 --> 00:13:42,200
at pagkatapos ay nawala ang bata.

242
00:13:42,880 --> 00:13:45,400
Sa labas ng mundo,

243
00:13:45,600 --> 00:13:47,200
nananatiling misteryoso ang mga pangyayaring ito.

244
00:13:47,520 --> 00:13:49,480
Kung isusumbong ko ito,

245
00:13:49,480 --> 00:13:52,080
maaaring nasa panganib ang iyong buhay
anumang oras.

246
00:13:53,160 --> 00:13:54,880
Paano isinalaysay ang kwento

247
00:13:56,880 --> 00:13:58,640
ay ganap na nasa akin.

248
00:14:00,480 --> 00:14:01,440
bigla akong natauhan

249
00:14:01,440 --> 00:14:03,760
na kung buntis ka
sa anak ni Xiao Xian

250
00:14:03,760 --> 00:14:05,240
at sinabing ito ay kay Prince Rui...

251
00:14:05,360 --> 00:14:06,160
Kamahalan,

252
00:14:06,320 --> 00:14:06,976
ikaw...

253
00:14:07,560 --> 00:14:08,560
Nakakabaliw ka.

